## Strategy Logic

*Indicators Used:*
- Supertrend (Period: 10, Multiplier: 3.5) 
- EMA (Period: 20)

*Entry Conditions:*
- *Long Position (Put Spread)*: Supertrend turns GREEN + Price above EMA
  - Sell Put (Delta ~-0.4) + Buy Put (Delta ~-0.25)
- *Short Position (Call Spread)*: Supertrend turns RED + Price below EMA  
  - Sell Call (Delta ~0.4) + Buy Call (Delta ~0.25)

*Exit Conditions:*
- Long position exits when Supertrend turns RED
- Short position exits when Supertrend turns GREEN
- Force exit 12 minutes before expiry

*Expiry Selection:*
- Monday-Thursday: Use next week expiry
- Friday: Use current week expiry

*Risk Management:*
- Uses spread strategies (limited risk)
- Delta-based option selection for consistent exposure
- Paper trading mode available for testing